era. No one
was surprised that the
Environmental Protection

44:02.340 --> 44:04.709 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
Agency was the focus.

44:04.742 --> 44:09.914 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
