The EPA should be open and
accountable to

44:21.025 --> 44:24.262 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
the American people and use
legitimate science.

44:24.295 --> 44:30.434 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
RUSH HOLT: Scientists are
fiercely independent.
They would resent horribly if
they felt their

44:30.468 --> 44:33.137 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
