at.

45:10.975 --> 45:16.047 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MILES O'BRIEN: While scientists
wait to see
what shoes might drop, a rumor
mill echoes

45:16.080 --> 45:18.616 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
