45:48.245 --> 45:50.815 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
KEITH COWING, NASA Watch: They
know where
the panic button is, and they
look at it once

45:50.848 --> 45:52.650 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
