45:52.683 --> 45:57.288 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MILES O'BRIEN: Keith Cowing is a
former NASA
biologist who founded the
watchdog Web site

45:57.321 --> 46:04.328 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
NASA Watch 20 years ago. He's
the proto-rogue,
and now he says everybody seems
to be joining

46:04.362 --> 46:06.230 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
in.

46:06.263 --> 46:09.967 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
KEITH COWING: Nobody has said,
shut that database
down, take that off your Web
site. But what's

46:10.001 --> 46:17.174 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
going to happen when you have
got this giant,
bubbling, simmering social media
crowd, and

46:17.208 --> 46:21.846 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
