things that
might happen to things that are
happening?

46:21.879 --> 46:24.548 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
There's a colossal hair trigger
waiting out
there.

46:24.582 --> 46:31.856 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MILES O'BRIEN: In the meantime,
data refuge
is as much therapeutic as it is
prophylactic.

46:31.889 --> 46:35.926 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Programmer Brendan O'Brien -- no
relation
-- showed me how they're doing
their work.

46:35.960 --> 46:39.697 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
BRENDAN O'BRIEN, Programmer: The
toughest
part about this is figuring out
what this

46:39.730 --> 46:44.935 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
