archive it in
a sensible form.

46:44.969 --> 46:51.075 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MILES O'BRIEN: Data refuge
organizers sent
questionnaires to 65,000
scientists to determine

46:51.108 --> 46:54.679 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
