task.

46:54.712 --> 47:00.951 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So far, they have received 7,500
responses.
As they march through the
databases, they

47:00.985 --> 47:07.425 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
are simultaneously developing
tools to organize
the effort, protect the
integrity of the data,

47:07.458 --> 47:09.827 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
and make an app for widespread
use.

47:09.860 --> 47:14.498 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
BRENDAN O'BRIEN: If we have the
foresight
to back the stuff up now, we may
be -- maybe

47:14.532 --> 47:16.333 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
later generations will thank us.

47:16.367 --> 47:21.338 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MILES O'BRIEN: Scientists are
also planning
a public campaign to save their
enterprise.

47:21.372 --> 47:29.080 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
