in that type
of situation.

51:52.176 --> 51:57.147 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
ANA LOPEZ: I debated with Nick,
like, a couple
months ago. And I get it. And I
can't put

51:57.181 --> 51:58.949 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
