51:58.983 --> 52:03.620 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But causing everybody else to
live in fear
like you is counterproductive.
People often

52:03.654 --> 52:11.061 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
forget that my university was
the site for
the first recorded mass shooting
in U.S. history.

52:11.095 --> 52:13.097 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
And that's usually brushed under
the rug.

52:13.130 --> 52:19.603 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
RAMIRO MARTINEZ, Retired Texas
Ranger: Here's
where some of the bullets hit.

52:19.636 --> 52:24.842 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
My name is Ramiro Martinez. Back
in 1966,
I was with the Austin Police
Department. Together,

52:24.875 --> 52:27.845 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
