down the sniper.

52:27.878 --> 52:35.819 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Right here is where he died.
And, at that
time, I started waving the
shotgun and hollering

52:35.853 --> 52:42.426 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
