they kept
shooting.

52:42.459 --> 52:51.001 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I have been asked about my
opinion about concealed
handgun campus carry. And I'm
against it.

52:51.035 --> 52:57.341 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So, we don't need young people,
who are just
a little over 21, probably a
little bit immature,

52:57.374 --> 53:00.244 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
