campus.

53:00.277 --> 53:05.649 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
NICK ROLAND: The reality is,
there are vastly
more guns in this country than
there are people.

53:05.682 --> 53:11.121 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
We're awash in guns. My solution
to that is
not to disarm the people that
aren't committing

53:11.155 --> 53:14.691 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
acts of violence. It's to give
them a chance
to defend themselves.

53:14.725 --> 53:19.563 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
RAMIRO MARTINEZ: If a citizen
had been out
here with a gun, and I saw him,
and I didn't

53:19.596 --> 53:24.334 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
know him from Adam, I might have
blasted him
away. Let the police do the
policing.

